name: Under Water Wicked
description:
The idea behind this artwork comes in my mind after i saw a stock image of a girl swimming and only half of her face is visible so instantly i get the idea what if there is a cursed lake and in that lake there is a under water Wicked who kills people who visit lake in night. 

So before creating this artwork , i created an imaginary story that what if ? there is a village called so and so had a cursed lake whomever goes to that cursed lake at night they never came back because there is a wicked under the water, who kills people and drink there blood to stay young forever. So one day a group of friends decided to viste the cursed lake at night and explore the lake they get flamethrower with theme after exploring they found that someone is with theme and they go deep inside the lake and they saw a wicked who are swimming towards them so they swim faster to the surface but wicked kill them all

So from this imaginary story i created a scene where there is wicked and a group of friends who are bagging to life there lifes and a fire of a flamethrower
